item.title: About
item.description: Hey there! My name is Mehti Musayev. I am from Saint Petersburg, Russia. Passionate about machine learning and software engineering.

item.title: Contact info
item.description: I am happy to communicate with smart people. You can reach me via email or telegram.

item.title: Projects
item.description: During my career I have been collaborating into limited number of open source projects. My volunteer work for open source community started in 2016 when I was using several projects at work. Here is the full list of open source projects where I am currently represented as a collaborator: RedBaron baron yapf (owned by Google) ELFI (owned by Aalto University)
